HEADWORD: Fagopyrum
<hw>Fagopyrum</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>a genus of plants of the
buckwheat family, including the buckwheat <spn>Fagopyrum
esculentum</spn>; in some classifications included in the genus
<gen>Polygonum</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Fagopyrum</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
